overview: Are you a college student looking to make money? Check out CampusHero.com, a site dedicated to having all the hottest campus representative jobs. Campus Hero was founded with one simple mission. Provide college students and organizations a way to generate income without leaving their prospective campuses. Our website focuses only on campus representative jobs and is far from your typical job listing website. Companies such as Microsoft, Apple, Disney, Red Bull, Sony, Jet Blue and hundreds of others are looking for students across the country to represent their products. You will not only earn money along with free prizes, but you will also be building your resume and experience at the same time. Many representatives go on to work full time for their prospective company. Campus Hero is designed so college students across the country can have more time and money in order to enjoy the best times of their lives. Go to CampusHero.com to start earning money today!
